name: Soviet Union graduation
description: “Wonderful school years…” — this was Varya’s thoughts when she had a photo session for her graduation album. Soon her last school Disko will be over and she’ll need to say goodbye to carefree childhood. For some reason everyone tells her: “who does not work shall not eat” and “night is not a hindrance to work”. Varenka will understand the true meaning of these slogans very soon, but for now she has youth, carelessness and big hopes for tomorrow.
